---
title: Crispy Shallot Beef Croquettes with Mash, Gravy and Sautéed Veggies
description: Big texture and bold taste are on the menu tonight! Beef and potato patties are breaded with a crushed crispy shallot coating, then baked to achieve that craveable crunch. The croquettes and a creamy mash are smothered in a velvety gravy, while sautéed zucchini and carrots round out the plate.
